cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "GreenRisk: Explainable Greenwashing-Risk Scoring for Corporate Climate Disclosures"
abstract: >-
  GreenRisk scores corporate climate-disclosure paragraphs for greenwashing
  risk on a 0-100 scale, combining pinned ClimateBERT signal classifiers with
  a Mamdani fuzzy rule base. Every score ships with an auditable
  rule-activation trace and a W3C PROV-O provenance graph binding the result
  to the exact model revisions and instrument version that produced it.
authors:
